data: {"arguments":{"hints":["VIP customers","customer","CustomerID","CompanyName","ranking","most","top"]},"name":"re_recall","result":{"candidateIntents":[],"contextMd":"## 已识别的数据上下文\n\n### 数据对象（Od）\n\n`Od:ORDER_ENT` **ORDER_ENT** [entity]: 订单实体，包含订单基本信息、客户关联、员工关联和运费等核心属性\n  matched[2|]{prop|type|desc|match|tier}:\n    CustomerID|text|\"\"|customer→col|PROP_NAME\n    CustomerID|text|\"\"|CustomerID→col|PROP_NAME\n  others[4|]{prop|desc}:\n    EmployeeID|\"\"\n    Freight|\"\"\n    OrderDate|\"\"\n    OrderID|\"\"\n\n`Od:CUSTOMER` **CUSTOMER** [entity]: 客户主数据，包含客户基本信息、联系方式和地理位置信息\n  others[11|]{prop|desc}:\n    Address|\"\"\n    City|\"\"\n    CompanyName|\"\"\n    ContactName|\"\"\n    ContactTitle|\"\"\n    Country|\"\"\n    CustomerID|\"\"\n    Fax|\"\"\n    Phone|\"\"\n    PostalCode|\"\"\n    Region|\"\"\n\n### 识别到的列引用（可作为 groupBy 维度）\n\ngroupBy[1|]{token|od|prop}:\n  customer|ORDER_ENT|CustomerID\n→ 建议 `groupBy: [\"CustomerID\"]`\n\n### smartquery 构造规则（强制）\n\n**filters 与 groupBy 不互斥，请同时返回**：\n- `filters` — 承载上文「筛选值」所有行（`prop`、`op`、`dbValue`），用于 WHERE 定位具体记录\n- `groupBy` — 承载上文「列引用」所有列 + `filters` 中命中的同一 prop（即使该 prop 已被 filter，也要列入 groupBy，保证结果里出现该维度列，便于用户读出语义和做对比）\n- 例：用户问「NA地区在所有GEO中的占比」→ `filters:[{prop:GEO,op:=,value:\"N.A.\"}]` **且** `groupBy:[\"GEO\", ...]`，全局分母由 Intent 的 `pivot_percent_scope=global` 处理\n- 仅当用户问题**完全不涉及**某类维度时（如纯粹「共有多少订单」无任何切片意图），才省略 groupBy\n\n### 操作提示\n\n以上属性描述已截断。调用 **lookup** 工具可获取完整的属性定义、Ok 知识条目和业务规则。\n\n","hintsResolution":"merged into recall token set","hintsUsed":["VIP customers","customer","CustomerID","CompanyName","ranking","most","top"],"totalTokens":7},"type":"function_call"}

